          <title>Chinese Tech Firm DeepSeek Accused of Copying ChatGPT Technology</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A Chinese tech firm, DeepSeek, is accused of copying the technology behind ChatGPT, a popular AI model developed by OpenAI. The allegations have sparked a reexamination of the assumptions that led to a panic in the US over DeepSeek's advancements.]]></description>
